This is the README file 

1. Change to the working directory

         cd Basic-Agri-Detection-main

2. Create a isolated Python Environment

         python -m venv venv

3. Activate that virtual environment. 

        .\venv\Scripts\activate

    Your prompt changes to (venv) to show itâ€™s active.

4. Read requirements.txt and install every listed package 

        pip install -r requirements.txt

5. Run the script on img1.jpg.

        python infer_image2.py img1.jpeg

     It prints the result and writes annotated_leaf.jpg in the same folder.

